title: Sinister Ministers Collared - Season 1
description:
Sinister Ministers Collared - Season 1

When we're at our lowest and most vulnerable, our ministers are the people we know will be there to lift us up and offer guidance. But what happens when your counselor becomes confused and abuses their moral authority? What happens when your minister - becomes sinister?

Ep 1 - Sacrament Of Evil
Ep 2 - Devil In Disguise
Ep 3 - Lambs To The Slaughter
